node.text:
Our friends over at @Classicdadmoves helped us celebrate the ultimate golf dad with all the Chili’s food and some ice cold @michelobultra - just in time for Father’s Day! 

Keep an eye out - we might just have an epic Father’s Day giveaway coming your way!

node.text: Now, when you grab a dad-sized bite at Chili’s, you’re doing it for a great cause. How? We partnered with @classicdadmoves & kids @stjude to help raise awareness (and money, too). Head to your local Chili’s today and #CreateAPepper But first, check out our IG story to see the kids imitate their dads.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chili's Grill & Bar on August 03, 2021.

node.text: CHILI’S GIRL SUMMER IS ABOUT TO BE LIT! Only a few more days to enter to win the most epic Chili’s Girl Summer getaway to Miami! Check out the link in bio 🌶☀️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chili's Grill & Bar on August 01, 2021. May be an image of drink, food and text.

node.text: Taking it easy is even easier when you’ve got our $5 Blackberry Tito-Rita by your side. Summer’s hottest flavor has officially arrived thanks to this premium ‘Rita made with @Titosvodka , @Lunazultequila Blanco, @Monin_usa Blackberry syrup, triple sec and fresh sour. We’re getting thirsty just thinking about it!

node.text: Summer is in full swing, and we’ve got just the ice-cold ‘Rita you need to keep your chill. Stay tuned for our announcement of August’s $5 Marg of the Month!

node.text: Pour up a celebration on #NationalTequilaDay with with $5 Frose and Captain’s Stay-Cay ‘Ritas, $6 Presidente Margaritas, or take the refresh-tivities anywhere with a $30 Margarita Gallon Bag. Party at our place or get them To-Go all day long on 7/24!
